English: Dithokgwa ga e no ba mehlaka ya di mangrove - di akaretša a mangwe a mafelo a mafelelo a mafelo a boemo bja mašhoka a maaatla ao a kilego a khupetša molala wa Gangetic. 
Category:Mangrove
